    <briefdescription>
<para>ZMQ PUB sink for generated IQ (Phase B). </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Streams cf32 blocks (from synth or the composer) to a ZMQ PUB endpoint using doppler&apos;s <computeroutput>dp_pub_*</computeroutput> wire layer (SIGS header, magic &quot;SIGS&quot;), converting to the requested wire sample type per block. This is the <computeroutput>--output zmq://…</computeroutput> destination; a <computeroutput>dp_sub_*</computeroutput> receiver (e.g. examples/c/spectrum_analyzer) reads the stream.</para>
<para>Lifecycle: wfm_zmq_sink_open -&gt; wfm_zmq_sink_send* -&gt; wfm_zmq_sink_close</para>
<para><programlisting><codeline><highlight class="normal"><ref refid="wfm__sink_8h_1aa71743d6b829827a632162c0fa105691" kindref="member">wfm_zmq_sink_t</ref><sp/>*s<sp/>=<sp/><ref refid="wfm__sink_8h_1a1400add436d1f06183482eeec035e703" kindref="member">wfm_zmq_sink_open</ref>(</highlight><highlight class="stringliteral">&quot;tcp://0.0.0.0:5555&quot;</highlight><highlight class="normal">,<sp/>3);<sp/></highlight><highlight class="comment">//<sp/>ci16</highlight><highlight class="normal"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><ref refid="wfm__sink_8h_1a44631e5112e25f08491dffd0b9830295" kindref="member">wfm_zmq_sink_send</ref>(s,<sp/>iq,<sp/>4096,<sp/>1e6,<sp/>2.4e9);</highlight></codeline>
<codeline><highlight class="normal"><ref refid="wfm__sink_8h_1a3f879775e253bba43c97837ced4e5485" kindref="member">wfm_zmq_sink_close</ref>(s);</highlight></codeline>
</programlisting> </para>
    </detaileddescription>
